### Hash (#) qualifier
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "addresses": [
    "#5 100 Wellington St, Ottawa, ON K1A 0A9"
  ]
}

###

### Room qualifier — hotel room stripped before geocoding
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "addresses": [
    "Room 412 Fairmont Royal York, 100 Front St W, Toronto, ON M5J 1E3",
    "Room 204 Sheraton Vancouver Wall Centre, 1088 Burrard St, Vancouver, BC V6Z 2R9",
    "Room 101 Hotel Nelligan, 106 Rue Saint-Paul O, Montreal, QC H2Y 1Z3"
  ]
}

###

### Postal code fallback — fake street, real postal code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "addresses": [
    "99999 Nowhere Blvd, Apt 12, Toronto, ON M5V 3A8"
  ]
}

###

### Not found — fake street and no valid postal code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "addresses": [
    "Unit 5 99999 Nowhere Blvd, Faketown, ON"
  ]
}

