###

### Duplicate addresses — same address 4 ways, should result in 1 Nominatim call
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "addresses": [
    "100 Queen St W, Toronto, ON M5H 2N2",
    "100 Queen St W, Toronto, ON M5H 2N2",
    "Apt 3 100 Queen St W, Toronto, ON M5H 2N2",
    "Unit 7 100 Queen St W, Toronto, ON M5H 2N2"
  ]
}
